name: Noise à Noise 19 [5/9]
description:
This tile-series is designed for the first compilation album for the label with the same name for experimental and noise music. These tiles match together to form a total image [and can be collected to fit together]. This piece contains manipulated Polkadot2d noise by reaction-diffusion blur reaction.

Earnings from these sets are to be spent on the funding of next productions for this super-independent movement.
